Documentation.Documentation: The SCD NAV must run daily Mon to Fri and on the last day of the month. This job runs on the last day of the month. It check if that day is a weekday or a weekend day. If a weekday the plan exits and no further action is taken. If a weekend day the plan triggers SCD_EOD_PROCESSING.

Variable.Name: Script
Variable.Value:
$inputDate = "${vl_EFFECTIVE_DATE}" $today = [datetime]::ParseExact($inputDate, "yyyyMMdd", $null)
Write-Host "Today's Date is :" $today.ToString("yyyy-MM-dd")
$day = $today.ToString("ddd")
Write-Host "Today is a" $day
if (($day -eq "Sat") -Or ($day -eq "Sun")) { $Weekend = "Y" $exitCode = "1" } else { $Weekend = "N" $exitCode = "0" }
Write-Host "Is today's date a weekend?" $Weekend
exit $exitCode
